&lt;li class=&quot;li4&quot;&gt;Implement new corporate legal workflows and processes using AI technology&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li4&quot;&gt;Manage outside counsel and internal cross-functional stakeholders in connection with complex corporate projects.&lt;/li&gt;
