&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About The Team:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Come join our growing Corporate IT team to architect and scale the technology foundation that powers Dynamic Work for our employees. As a Corporate IT Architect, you will focus on designing and evolving a secure, automated, and scalable internal IT ecosystem that delivers world-class technology experiences across our workforce and workspaces.&lt;/p&gt;
