&lt;li&gt;Architect and mature Service Desk processes (incident, request, problem, change) with automation and self-service at the core.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement AI Service Desk using LLMs and Virtual Agents for intelligent ticket routing, automated triage, and instant user resolution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engineer end-to-end automation frameworks that transform manual support interventions into &quot;self-healing&quot; workflows&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design modern endpoint management strategy across macOS and Windows using Jamf and Intune&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish patching, compliance, and configuration baselines with measurable enforcement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own architecture and governance for Google Workspace, Slack, Zoom, and conference room AV systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with partner teams to automate onboarding/offboarding workflows across integrated systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Security to implement zero-trust principles and maintain audit readiness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive API-first integrations across platforms to reduce manual intervention.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Rationalize tooling, manage vendor strategy, and optimize spend.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead escalations and provide architectural oversight for complex cross-platform issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document standards, integration patterns, and lifecycle management strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
