&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10+ years in Corporate IT, Endpoint Engineering, or IT Architecture roles within distributed or high-growth environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep expertise in Jamf Pro and Microsoft Intune.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong administrative and architectural experience with Google Workspace, Slack, Zoom, and SaaS ecosystems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience designing zero-touch device lifecycle management programs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge of identity and access management (Okta, Azure AD, or equivalent).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience implementing ITIL-aligned service management processes.&lt;/li&gt;
