&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Rubrik is seeking a Cyber Resilience Architect (Field CTO) to drive technical strategy and business leadership across the APJ region.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;In this role you will act as a transformation architect operating at the intersection of business strategy and technical execution. You will help large enterprises modernize their approach to Data Protection, Cyber Recovery, Identity Resilience, and AI-driven security and governance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are accountable for influencing regional revenue outcomes by leading high-impact discovery, shaping differentiated architectures, and guiding strategic account execution. You will evangelize and architect Rubrik’s portfolio across on-prem, cloud, SaaS, identity, cyber resilience, and AI solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Core Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Executive Advisory: Serve as a trusted advisor to CIOs, CISOs, and Board. Partner with CIOs on modern data protection, operational efficiency, and cloud strategy. Partner with CISOs on cyber resilience, identity protection, and breach recovery readiness. At the executive level, position data resilience as a board-level priority — aligning Rubrik’s platform to measurable outcomes such as operational continuity, risk reduction, regulatory compliance, and AI readiness.&lt;/li&gt;
