&lt;li&gt;Deal Orchestration: Master the MEDDIC framework to qualify opportunities, identifying technical &quot;champions&quot; and neutralizing competitive threats through superior architecture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Product Liaison: Distill complex field requirements into actionable insights for the Product Management team, ensuring the APJ voice influences our global roadmap.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical Leadership: Design integrated solutions across On-Prem, SaaS, Identity, and Multi-Cloud environments, with a specific focus on Cyber Security including designing isolated recovery environments (IRE) and clean room recovery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Market Evangelism: Represent Rubrik at select industry events and executive forums. Contribute to thought leadership initiatives and support key marketing engagements as needed. This is an important but limited portion of the role, with primary focus remaining on strategic account execution and revenue impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
