&lt;h4 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Director, Field Marketing Asia Pacific &amp;amp; Japan (APJ)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you a natural connector who lights up a room, can strategize a go-to-market across cultures, and knows how to turn big ideas into pipeline? Then this might be the opportunity for you. We are looking for a senior marketing leader who knows APJ not just as a geography, but as a collection of cultures, relationships, and ways of doing business.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;About the role&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reporting to the International Director of Marketing, you&#39;ll own the full field marketing motion across Asia Pacific and Japan — setting strategy, leading a regional team, and driving pipeline growth across diverse markets and channels.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll represent APJ at the global table while staying deeply connected to what&#39;s happening on the ground. That balance between global alignment and local relevance is where this role lives and succeeds. You&#39;ll work in close partnership with Sales, Inside Sales, and Partner Sales, leading with vision, empathy, and accountability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute integrated, data-driven marketing plans that drive measurable pipeline growth across APJ&#39;s diverse markets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead, mentor, and develop a regional team of skilled field marketers, in a high-performance culture built on trust and collaboration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate global priorities into locally resonant programmes across markets as distinct as Japan, India, ASEAN, and ANZ.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain strong relationships with sales leadership across the region, acting as a true strategic partner.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and run the full demand generation mix: partner marketing, field events, regional pipeline generation programs for scalability, and own the relationship with global marketing functions such as digital marketing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the regional budget, track performance rigorously via Salesforce and Tableau, and continuously optimize for impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience You’ll Need:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7+ years B2B marketing in a leadership role, with field or regional marketing leadership experience in high-growth technology companies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep, first-hand knowledge of the APJ region, its markets, its stakeholders, and how to navigate both.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A track record of building meaningful relationships across sales, partners, and global teams and delivering results through them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience leading integrated marketing programmes in a high growth market, balancing tailored programs with high growth programs to drive demand generation, and deliver a strong through partner marketing motion for scalability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong strategic thinking paired with a hands-on approach and a bias for action.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Compelling communication and influencing skills across cultures, seniority levels, and functions and a leadership style rooted in empathy, clarity, and an ability to bring out the best in others.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why this role?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;APJ is one of our highest-growth regions, Cyber resilience isn&#39;t a nice-to-have anymore. It&#39;s mission-critical. Rubrik helps the world&#39;s leading organisations protect their data, withstand attacks, and recover with confidence. We&#39;re growing fast and expanding aggressively across APJ. This is a pivotal role in shaping that growth trajectory and the go to market strategy that drives it. You&#39;ll have a clear goal and mandate, and the full support of a global marketing organisation behind you. If this speaks to you, we’d l

&lt;h2&gt;About the role:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rubrik is looking for a visionary, high-impact &lt;strong&gt;Director of Web Marketing &lt;/strong&gt;to act as the strategic architect and executive champion for our global digital presence. This is a &lt;strong&gt;&quot;player-director&quot;&lt;/strong&gt; role designed for a leader who can navigate high-level corporate strategy while maintaining the technical curiosity to jump into the trenches alongside their team. You will be the resident expert for all things web, bridging the gap between the Head of Digital Marketing’s vision and IT’s technical execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We aren&#39;t looking for a &quot;maintainer&quot;—we are looking for a &lt;strong&gt;transformative leader&lt;/strong&gt;. You are a relentless critical thinker who continuously questions the status quo and isn&#39;t afraid to ask &quot;why&quot; to drive meaningful change. You will lead a unified web organization by coaching our expert leads in &lt;strong&gt;Web Performance&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Web Production&lt;/strong&gt;, empowering them to leverage Generative AI and advanced automation to scale our content, personalize user journeys, and stay ahead of the curve. Your role is to filter the &quot;noise&quot; of technical complexity into a clear, strategic narrative for Rubrik’s executive leadership. This role reports into our HQ in Palo Alto, 3x per week.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What you&#39;ll do:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Executive Advocacy &amp;amp; Strategic Alignment:&lt;/strong&gt; Serve as the primary voice for the Web team at the leadership level; secure the resources and alignment needed for our domain experts to execute world-class work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI-Driven Innovation: &lt;/strong&gt;Champion the use of Generative AI for content scaling, AI-driven personalization to tailor the user journey, and next-gen AI tools to supercharge SEO and Conversion Rate Optimization (CRO).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transformative Thinking:&lt;/strong&gt; Deeply analyze existing processes to identify friction points. You are expected to challenge &quot;how we’ve always done it&quot; to build a more efficient, high-performance digital engine.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Storytelling &amp;amp; Distillation:&lt;/strong&gt; Take the high-volume output of the production and performance teams and distill it into a high-level narrative for executive leadership, focusing on business impact and long-term vision.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team Enablement &amp;amp; Coaching:&lt;/strong&gt; Empower and coach your leads to own their reporting and cross-functional relationships. You provide the mentorship and frameworks they need to showcase their wins to the broader organization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic IT Liaison:&lt;/strong&gt; Act as the primary business stakeholder for IT, ensuring our technical architecture is world-class, scalable, and built to support the future of AI-integrated web experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operational Partnership:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead from the front. While you own the strategy and coaching, you are ready to roll up your sleeves—whether helping the production team navigate a high-velocity launch or assisting the performance team in diagnosing a complex tracking issue.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Experience you&#39;ll need:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;12+ years of experience&lt;/strong&gt; in web strategy or digital leadership, with a track record of leading high-performing teams in a high-growth B2B SaaS environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The &quot;Why&quot; Factor:&lt;/strong&gt; A critical thinking mindset with a proven ability to interrogate workflows and drive transformative change in complex organizations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Literacy:&lt;/strong&gt; Practical experience or a deep strategic understanding

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Director, Product Design&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: &lt;/strong&gt;Palo Alto, US&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;About Rubrik&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join the public powerhouse that is securing the future of AI.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rubrik has officially entered a new era. Fresh off a &lt;strong&gt;headline-making successful IPO &lt;/strong&gt;and boasting over &lt;strong&gt;$1.57 Billion in ARR&lt;/strong&gt;, we have the market stability of a giant and the hunger of a startup. We’ve already conquered Data Security—now, we are pivoting to our most ambitious mission yet: &lt;strong&gt;Securing and Accelerating the World&#39;s AI Transformation.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a &lt;strong&gt;Director, Product Design&lt;/strong&gt; at Rubrik, you will be pioneering the next generation of User Experiences for the enterprise! From AI to air-gapped immutable backups to defending against ransomware, our tech stack is the definition of cyber resilience. We are a &lt;strong&gt;Gartner Magic Quadrant Leader&lt;/strong&gt; and a winner of the &lt;strong&gt;Red Dot &amp;amp; &lt;/strong&gt;back-to-back&lt;strong&gt; iF Design Awards &lt;/strong&gt;because we believe security and protection should be powerful and usable. Come build the safety net for the AI generation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Team &amp;amp; Role:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our design team is strong and mighty, with about 60 amazing individuals from all walks of the industry and life located worldwide. As our company and our products grow rapidly, it is crucial to scale the experience of our product and our design team in the right way and with the right people. Every hire counts!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Director, Product Design&lt;/strong&gt; for our Palo Alto site. This is a pivotal leadership role where you will not only oversee a talented team of designers but also serve as a strategic partner to Engineering and Product leadership to make Rubrik the benchmark for enterprise design.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sneak peek into our product:&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F9949Q-_onc&amp;amp;t=9s&quot;&gt; https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F9949Q-_onc&amp;amp;t=9s&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.rubrik.com/company/newsroom/press-releases/23/rubrik-security-cloud-named-a-winner-of-the-prestigious-2023-red-dot-design-award&quot;&gt;Red Dot Design Award&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://ifdesign.com/en/winner-ranking/project/rubrik-security-cloud/618120&quot;&gt;iF Design Award&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://medium.com/rubrik-design&quot;&gt;Rubrik Design Medium Page&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build &amp;amp; Lead High-Performing Teams:&lt;/strong&gt; Recruit, mentor, and retain a world-class team of designers. You’ll be responsible for their career growth, providing coaching on both craft and navigational &quot;soft&quot; skills to help them scale their impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Define Strategic Vision:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner with VP and Director-level leadership in Product Management and Engineering to define the long-term roadmap. You’ll transform high-level business goals into actionable design strategies that balance immediate needs with a &quot;North Star&quot; vision.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Champion Design Excellence: &lt;/strong&gt;Ensure all team deliverables meet the highest standards of craft, usability, and visual consistency across the product.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive Operational Excellence:&lt;/strong&gt; Establish and refine design processes that allow the team to move fast wi

&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Director,&amp;nbsp; Product Management, Data Threat Analytics&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: Palo Alto, CA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;The Product Management team at Rubrik drives Rubrik’s vision forward, ensuring we continue to secure the world’s data by delivering on our market-leading platform to address our customers’ most challenging data management &amp;amp; security needs. Our Product Managers are responsible for guiding multidisciplinary teams towards the goal of shipping high-quality products on time. We wear multiple hats throughout the different stages in the product lifecycle and set the vision for our growing family of products. As advocates for both our users and our business, Product Managers balance varied perspectives and empower their teams to do great work.&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role requires a leader who can set a compelling strategy, align diverse teams, and turn complex recovery problems into clear, actionable outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For this, we are seeking a Director of Product Management -&amp;nbsp; Data Threat Analytics with a strong hybrid and cloud security background to lead a product area (and PMs) focused on detecting and understanding threats against sensitive data in hybrid&amp;nbsp; and cloud environments - with recovery as the end goal. This role owns anomaly detection, threat hunting, monitoring, and sensitive data discovery on backed-up data, and will help reimagine cyber recovery for hybrid and modern cloud architectures.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Own:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Strategy:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and own the long-term product vision for data threat analytics anchored in hybrid, and cloud-native environments, and recovery-first outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reimagine how threat signals, anomaly detection, and sensitive data discovery directly inform - blast radius assessment, clean restore point selection and how this feeds into confident cyber recovery workflows&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop a point of view on the evolving hybrid and cloud threat landscape, including ransomware, and misconfigurations - and translate into differentiated product strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Execution Excellence:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive end-to-end execution for recovery across matrix organization and own the process from concept validation to GA and customer adoption while holding the upstream teams accountable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Break-down ambiguous, multi-year product bets into clear milestones, measurable outcomes, and incremental value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish strong product operating rhythms - with tight roadmap discipline and backlog hygiene&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;People &amp;amp; Org Leadership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build, lead and scale a high-performing team of Product Managers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach PMs to think beyond feature delivery toward - problem framing, systems thinking and recovery outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop PM talent with strong focus on structured thinking and crisp communication, executive-ready storytelling and customer-centric results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster a culture of high accountability with stakeholders and build teams that move fast, learn, and course-correct.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create clarity in a complex org by defining ownership boundaries, decision-making frameworks, and clear interfaces with engineering, snappable PMs, data science and security research.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT RUBRIK&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rubrik is on a mission to secure the world&#39;s data. As a leader in Zero Trust Data Security™, Rubrik helps organizations across industries achieve business resilience against cyberattacks, malicious insiders, and operational disruptions. Our platform delivers data security posture, data threat analytics, data observability, and data recovery — enabling teams to protect data wherever it lives: on-premises, in the cloud, or at the edge.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;POSITION SUMMARY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Email Marketing Manager will be a critical contributor within Rubrik&#39;s Digital Marketing team, owning end-to-end execution of email marketing programs that drive pipeline and revenue. Sitting at the intersection of demand generation and digital media, this role is responsible for email nurture strategy, batch/blast campaigns, paid email placements, paid digital advertising support, and paid newsletter sponsorships. The ideal candidate is a data-driven marketer who thrives in a fast-paced, collaborative environment and brings a strong command of marketing automation, analytics, and cross-functional execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Email Nurture Programs&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Design, build, and optimize multi-touch email nurture sequences that guide prospects through the buyer journey.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Partner with content, demand gen, and sales development to develop audience segmentation and personalization strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Monitor engagement metrics and apply A/B testing to continuously improve open rates, click-through rates, and conversion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Email Blasts &amp;amp; Campaign Execution&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Manage end-to-end production and deployment of batch email campaigns, including list segmentation, QA, scheduling, and reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Coordinate with field marketing, content, and product teams to align email sends with campaign calendars and product launches.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Ensure all campaigns adhere to CAN-SPAM, GDPR, and other applicable email compliance standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Paid Email &amp;amp; Paid Newsletters&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Own Rubrik&#39;s paid email placements with third-party publishers and media vendors, including negotiating placements, briefing creative, and measuring ROI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Manage paid newsletter sponsorships across industry publications targeting security, IT, and cloud audiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Track spend, pacing, and performance across paid email programs and report results to stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Paid Ads Support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Collaborate with the paid media team to align email and paid ad messaging, landing pages, and audience targeting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Support retargeting and account-based programs that span email and paid channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
